â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ FAM001.wombat.*.tsv (WOMBAT analysis files)
â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   â””â”€â”€ FAM001.dnm.*.tsv (DNM analysis files)
â”‚   â”‚       â””â”€â”€ FAM002/
